{"id": "ChIJkXzsEADHwoARp4VxsuPQJ0o", "rating": 5, "userRatingCount": 17, "displayName": {"text": "LTTT (Little Tokyo Table Tennis)", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJkXzsEADHwoARp4VxsuPQJ0o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wR1lYQTBibXBWVERka2NWZDRVREpxVVZOak9GRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing decor, really nice offerings and the atmosphere and vibe are cool! Ended up picking up two hats and the staff were super laid back and chill! It really felt like a cool place for people to hangout and they had a dj playing music while they were projecting table tennis matches. Super cool store!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing decor, really nice offerings and the atmosphere and vibe are cool! Ended up picking up two hats and the staff were super laid back and chill! It really felt like a cool place for people to hangout and they had a dj playing music while they were projecting table tennis matches. Super cool store!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Eric Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108016508560805263132/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAMzuv1wf3SZZ0Y3XZzgGRKHCNf_CtvyaaLV1igxa0mFVhx2Xx=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T17:21:46.617896916Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wR1lYQTBibXBWVERka2NWZDRVREpxVVZOak9GRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wR1lYQTBibXBWVERka2NWZDRVREpxVVZOak9GRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70010ec7c91:0x4a27d0e3b27185a7"}, {"name": "places/ChIJkXzsEADHwoARp4VxsuPQJ0o/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN6eEtuRVh3EAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "If you’re a fan of their table tennis club held at Terasaki Budokan gym every Tuesday, you’ll be in he